00:01:27,690 --> 00:01:29,862
But the point is that it's
multiplied just by y.

31
00:01:29,862 --> 00:01:32,570

32
00:01:32,570 --> 00:01:35,480
And then it can equal some
arbitrary function q of x on

33
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,230
the right-hand side.

34
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:39,440
So every first order linear
equation can be

35
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,690
