67
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:25,980
That sometimes we can get
lucky and do a nonlinear

68
00:03:25,980 --> 00:03:29,190
transformation and convert a
nonlinear equation into a

69
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:30,440
linear one.

70
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:36,020

71
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:49,560
