79
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:20,200
But of course, we can
multiply through by

80
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:22,820
y and rewrite things.

81
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:25,430

82
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:29,220
And of course, this equation is
