00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:32,160
squared y equals 0.

84
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:39,580
Which again, is linear because
p of t can be identified with

85
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:45,120
negative t squared and q of t
can be identified with 0.

86
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:58,470
And then lastly, for part 5,
we have x squared y y prime

87
00:04:58,470 --> 00:05:04,780
plus 4x equals x cubed.

88
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:07,320

89
00:05:07,320 --> 00:05:09,880
And again, if we were to try
